channel.title: Selling Axoloti Board / Marketplace
channel.description:
Hi,
due to lack of time i would like to sell my Axoloti Board with Laser Cut Case and Cables. Its a great piece of Kit but requires time that i do not have at this point. Therefore i was wondering if it is cool to do so on the forum and if there is a category/place to do so ? Dont want to be rude but could not find any info on this topic.
Thank you
Markus
